Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you just have to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words lured men\Nto the Grand Line in pursuit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,of dreams greater than they've\Never dared to imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.29,0:00:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time known\Nas the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.50,0:00:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.09,0:00:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.85,0:00:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.10,0:01:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.57,0:01:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.82,0:01:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.83,0:01:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.58,0:01:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.30,0:01:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:02:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN A chuckles]\NAnother big haul today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's two in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN C]\NAll of this should keep Buggy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,from getting too mad at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN B]\NHey..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that boat out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We should check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN chuckling]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... It's a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN A chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,0:02:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]\NUh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me I'm not\Ndreaming this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...finding help out here\Nin the middle of nowhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're real, then please,\Ncould you get me some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.14,0:03:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you as much jewelry\Nand valuables as you like,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,if you could just give\Nme one little drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No sweat. We'll help ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But not until we see what kinda\Ntreasure you're holding on to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN C]\NYeah, don't mind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,--We'll just be a minute.\N--[HENCHMAN B laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN A]\NCan't get the damn thing open.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Hold up, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want, you can\Nkeep the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's our boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You tricked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,From the look of those clouds\Nmoving in from the south,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say a cold front's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can probably\Nexpect strong winds
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and squalls any\Ntime now, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, in that small a boat,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you run a bit of a\Nchance of capsizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:04:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]\NBingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just take whatever\Ntreasure you guys got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN A]\NGet back here, you bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN C]\NWe'll get you for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] "Luffy's Past!\NEnter Red-Haired Shanks!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI'm so hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] When the hell are\Nwe gonna reach land anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWho knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just sailin' on\Nthe wind and the waves,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,goin' where they take us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We might not ever\Neven reach the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I guess we will someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you find it dumb
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that someone trying to be\NKing of the Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't have a single\Nnavigational skill?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I just drift around...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you some famous bounty\Nhunter who's sailed the seas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any recollection
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of ever calling myself\Na bounty hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I set out onto the open sea\Nin search of just one man,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but then I couldn't\Nget back to my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,By that point, I had no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but to go after pirate\Nships to earn a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. So you're just lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't put it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, not my Shanks hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This straw hat means more to me\Nthan you could possibly know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been with me\Nin many a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something so precious
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that I couldn't even\Ngive to you, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta take me with you on\Nyour next adventure, Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna be a pirate\Njust like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, as if you\Ncould ever be a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhy couldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be a good\Nswimmer and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but that doesn't mean you'd\Nmake a good pirate, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NBut I'm a great fighter, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My punches are like two pistols!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NAre they now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that's supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs] He means that\Nyou're too much of a kid, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's right, you know.\NI got boys older than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a grown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS] Here, have some\Njuice and calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Thanks, Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing] I don't know one\Npirate who drinks juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a cheap shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA]\NExcuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA] So these are what pass\Nfor pirates around these parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks rather sad to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAKINO]\NWelcome, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're mountain bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But we didn't come here\Nto tear your place apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All we want is some sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say ten barrels should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but actually we're fresh\Nout of sake right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA]\NHm, Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,These other pirates seem\Nto still be drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that water in their glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that just happens to be the\Nlast of what I had stocked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NMy apologies, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like me and my friends\Ndrank the whole place dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have this if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't even been opened yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAKINO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an eight million\Nberry bounty on my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,One bottle isn't\Nenough for a nightcap,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so don't insult me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just great...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the floor's wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, Makino.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a rag I can\Nclean this up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAKINO]\NAh... Oh, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[glass shatters]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA] Since you like\Nto clean things so much
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe you'll find this\Nmess more fulfilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA]\NTa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A place with no sake is a place\Nnot worth our time, men.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, pansies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a problem in\Nthe world, Makino.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,--[SHANKS chuckles]\N--[PIRATES laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That fella really\Ngot you good, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE Q]\NTalk about a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you all laughing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've\Nfought back, Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter\Nhow strong they look
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,or how many of them there are,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,if you just laugh it off,\Nyou're not a man
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.77,0:09:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,or a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Luffy, I know\Nhow you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But the guy just\Nspilled some booze on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not worth getting\Nbent out of shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,--[MAKINO, SHANKS laugh]\N--[chomp]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS laughs] You shouldn't\Neat out of frustration, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NWait! What're you eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You didn't--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you ate the fruit\Nthat was inside that box?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NUh... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS] Spit it out\Nright now! Every single bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhat're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why're you shaking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, you just ate\Nthe Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,part of a group called\Nthe Devil Fruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating any of them takes away
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,your ability to swim for\Nthe rest of your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but the one you ate also\Nturns your body to rubber!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NNo way! It can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NYou dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAKINO panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA]\NWhat is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We were drinking and\Nhaving a nice time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...until you showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No one messes with Shanks' crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAKINO panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA] I don't think I said\Nanything to offend you directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYou think wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayor! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAYOR]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[BANDIT A laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[BANDIT A] Did you see the\Nlooks on those pirate's faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--[BANDIT A laughing]\N--[BANDIT B] Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They got doused in liquor\Nand didn't even say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA] Pirates are a\Nbuncha wimps, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all talk, no action.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NStop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Stop making fun of\NShanks and his men right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not wimps at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAKINO]\NLuffy, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] You better stop right\Nnow, you stupid bandits!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAKINO, MAYOR pant, gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA] You should watch\Nyour flapping gums, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No one who's ever made me mad
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,has lived to tell the\Nhorrifying and painful tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAYOR]\NWait! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the boy go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAYOR]\NI don't know what he's done,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and I certainly don't intend\Nto fight you over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll accept, I'll\Neven pay you to stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just spare the poor\Nboy's life, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,While the oldest generation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,may know the way of the\Nworld better than us all,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but this rotten\Nkid's already made me angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing can save him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the rotten\Nones around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're a lost cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...which you can regret\Nin the next life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,--[MAKINO] No!\N--[MAYOR] Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering why the bar\Nwas empty on such a fine day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAKINO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's the mountain\Nbandits again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA]\NEh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NShanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just now\Nshowing your heads?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been spending all this\Ntime scrubbing the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy. Didn't you say earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that your punches were\Nstronger than pistols?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I don't know what\Nyou think you're doing here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but you might wanna leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't want\Nsomething bad to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have just the man\Nto deliver this message.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll blow your head\Noff if I have to,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's up to you, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[BANDITS laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you risk your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that' you've\Ndrawn your pistol,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,are you willing to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are\Nyou talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that guns aren't for\Nthreats; they're for actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[BANDITS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAKINO, MAYOR gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You! You're a dead man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys fight dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did you think you\Nwere dealing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We never claimed to\Nbe saints or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You fellas are staring\Ndown a crew of pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We just want the boy, not you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NListen up, bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether I'm sprayed with\Nalcohol or doused with food,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,hell, even if I'm spit on,\Nmost of the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just laugh it off\Nand forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you hurt\Na friend of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll pay for it,\Nregardless of your reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NShanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're gonna pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Lousy pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill 'em all, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[BANDITS yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEN] I'll take care of this.\NShouldn't be a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[BANDITS yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,--[BEN grunts]\N--[BANDITS grunt, groan]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEN]\NYou shouldn't get too cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really wanted to fight\Nus, looks like a battleship
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,or something bigger\Nwoulda been more useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:14:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA stammers]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the kid who attacked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were\Na wanted man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A smokescreen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NLuffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I let that guy take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What're we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, calm down.\NQuit freakin' out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find him in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[BEN]\NHeh. What a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA] Looks like\NI made a clean getaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd never think to look
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,for a mountain bandit\Nescaping onto the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Dammit! Let go\Nof me, you dumbass idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I really hope you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] Yes, I know\Nthat's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're the one dying today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what I said\Nabout makin' me angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NDammit! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Filthy bandit scum and I\Ncouldn't squeeze off one hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY choking]\N--[HIGUMA laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA]\NSorry, kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't seem to have\Na use for you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA]\NWhat the-What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[choking]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[HIGUMA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NShanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[MONSTER whines]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NI'm in your debt, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Makino told me everything\Nabout how you stood up for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How you were willing to fight,\Nand put yourself on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a man now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But Shanks... your arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just an arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:17:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a nice extended vacation,\Nbut we have to part ways now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you'll miss me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but this time's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't beg you to\Ntake me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause I'm gonna\Nbecome a pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...all on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't take you\Nwith me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never make\Nit as a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make it as a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, I'm gonna gather a\Ncrew even better than yours
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm gonna find the\Ngreatest treasure in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I'll be\NKing of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha. You think you'll surpass us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NIn that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS]\NI'll leave this hat to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It means more to me than\Nanything in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,so you better take\Ngood care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:19:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[SHANKS] I want you to bring\Nthis hat back to me someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...in good condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And only once you've\Nbecome a great pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our promise, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NLuffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. You're gonna\Ndrop that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHeh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It is. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Uh. I am so hungry.\NIt's killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHey, look, a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Let's eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How do we catch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NLeave that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:20:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum... Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHelp me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You moron! What the\Nhell's goin' on now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN A]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN A gasps]\NHey, you there! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Men overboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Men overboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\NI find ship-wreckers
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop, you're just\Ngonna have to jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually impressed\Nyou made it onboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN]\NAre you trying to kill us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN A]\NStop the boat now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of us are members of\NBuggy the Clown's pirate crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This boat is ours now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry we had no idea
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.21,0:20:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you were the famous\NPirate Hunter Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN]\NPlease forgive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you three idiots,\NI lost sight of my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So just keep paddling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN]\NYes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll probably pull off\Nsomething once he spots land.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN C] So, any ideas\Nabout what we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.65,0:21:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN B]\NGood question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If Captain Buggy finds out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,a girl stole our boat and\Nour treasure, we're history.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN A]\NI know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHuh? So who is this Buggy guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN A] Uh. You've never\Nheard of Buggy the Clown?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NNope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the ruthless captain\Nof our pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's eaten one\Nof the Devil Fruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Above everything else, he is\Na one truly terrifying man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]\NYes, I've finally got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:21:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey girl, get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You better give us\Nthat map back or else!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN D] We just stole\Nthat chart of the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.99,0:22:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It belongs to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.91,0:22:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't get that thing back,\Nthen we're as good as dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be killed by one of\Nthe Captain's cannonballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.71,0:22:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN G]\NCaptain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've spotted something high\Nin the sky above the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NWell, shoot it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[cannon fires]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.22,0:22:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.39,0:22:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.81,0:22:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.27,0:22:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What... was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy fell from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Dammit, why were there\Ncannonballs flying at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.91,0:22:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NAt least I'm safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.54,0:22:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.25,0:22:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...what just happened\Nto me was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.89,0:23:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.78,0:23:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.49,0:23:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.99,0:23:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.62,0:23:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.71,0:23:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.63,0:23:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.26,0:23:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.56,0:23:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.40,0:24:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.40,0:24:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.66,0:24:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.53,0:24:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.13,0:24:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHow can any human being
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.71,0:24:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,be alive and chopped up\Nat the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.18,0:24:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] You're a rubber guy.\NHow human do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.09,0:24:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]\NNothing makes sense anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.68,0:24:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A rubber guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.60,0:24:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,some chopped up guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.85,0:24:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,who are these people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.56,0:24:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NUh... Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.98,0:24:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]\NNo! That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.94,0:24:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.69,0:24:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.48,0:24:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Terrifying Mysterious Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.69,0:24:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Buggy,\Nthe Clown Pirate!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.74,0:24:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

